description:
Deadline LIVE with Jack Blood

2010-05-19 (Wed)
----------------

Jack is live today covering the topics that matter most. Most of the first hour is spent covering the Rand Paul primary win in Kentucky. After that Jack Talks with Darren Craddock of Enerfood. In the second hour Jack is joined by Daniel Miller the President of the Texas Nationalist Movement.
